              Total Revenue
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant='h5' color='initial'>
              $580.00
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant='body2' color='initial'>
              $235.00 This month

      </Grid>

      <Chart />
      <Typography variant='body1' textAlign='center' padding={4}>

          Revenue Report
        </Button>
      </Typography>
    </>
  );
};

export default TrafficConversion;
